author: vmote
msg: Make StructureHandler and most of its methods abstract. It is never instantiated, has a bunch of empty classes that appear to be patterns. If those classes were to be filled in with logic, it would create problems in the subclasses. Also, any changes to signature now in the subclasses will cause the parent method to be used, which is probably not what would be wanted.
